query:
DELETE t1 FROM subTasks t1
INNER JOIN subTasks t2 
WHERE t1.workflowStepId = 210005 
  AND t2.workflowStepId = 210005
  AND t1.subTaskId = t2.subTaskId 
  AND t1.id > t2.id
  AND t1.completed = 0;
